{"tid":1500612,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"職工盟下周一到國泰城集會 國泰：屬禁制令涵蓋範圍","createTime":"2019-08-24T05:32:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T07:41:02.000Z","uid":59815,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7fd047b4a24ef7bce01cc4e0959d123aa2311c8d","tid":1500612,"uid":59815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T05:32:53.000Z","msg":"職工盟下周一到國泰城集會 國泰：屬禁制令涵蓋範圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n國泰航空表示，知悉職工盟計劃星期一下午在國泰城舉行集會活動，公司已提醒員工，機管局已獲批的禁制令亦涵蓋國泰城範圍，又向員工重申，對於任何支持或參與非法示威、暴力或過於激進的行為，均採取零容忍態度。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n國泰說，國泰城是公司全球營運總部，當中包括支援航班運作至關重要的設施，任何影響安全營運的活動，不但嚴重阻礙市民出行，亦會對公司的顧客及員工安全造成威脅，同時破壞香港經濟及香港國際機場的聲譽。<br />\n<br />\n國泰重申，公司全力支持維護《基本法》所賦予的一切權利和自由，國泰是一間營運遍佈全球的國際航空公司，必須遵守航班飛往及飛越國家及地區，包括中國內地的所有適用法規。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1476479-20190824.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1476479-20190824.htm&d=LRWPp57H9HH2b7ruXTkGLtLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=bc2479af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1476479-20190824.htm&h=16d96a70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1476479-20190824.htm</a><br />\n2019-08-24 12:53:05<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c321889bb5ec7ec29acb0523d4a73eaa08ac2e57","tid":1500612,"uid":59815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T07:41:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}